{"tid":1944345,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[易碎]生化危機 3 重製版保險箱密碼為「918」中國玩家感覺冒犯揚言抵制","createTime":"2020-03-26T10:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T11:08:54.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b0d6002efa53878d18c80489248a149f77bae873","tid":1944345,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:14:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/26/biohazard-re3-918/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F26%2Fbiohazard-re3-918%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2FCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=408418b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/26/biohazard-re3-918/game-channel/</a><br />\n<br />\n近日 Capcom 推出了《生化危機 3 重製版》的試玩版，以讓大家體驗重製版與舊作的分別。不過，有中國玩家遊玩過後指，遊戲內的密碼數字有冒犯中國之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ae5924c0-6db4-11ea-a6fd-84401f5f4161-scaled.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2Fae5924c0-6db4-11ea-a6fd-84401f5f4161-scaled.jpeg&h=657a4da9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《生化危機 3 重製版》試玩版的遊玩時間只有 5 分鐘左右，當中有個關卡需要在保險箱上輸入密碼，而密碼提示印在一張海報上，玩家推測後可得出三位密碼「918」。<br />\n<br />\n有中國玩家就指此數字讓其聯想到被日軍侵占的九一八事變，直感冒犯。更有中國玩家表示，如正式版未有對此作出修正，便會作出給《還願》和《我的英雄學院》一樣的差評。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-26-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.10.50-1280x576.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-26-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.10.50-1280x576.png&h=b91930d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，不少中國玩家與台灣玩家都認為這件事情過於牽強，並質疑是否與中國歷史有關的數字，如「64」、「128」等都通通不能使用，指某部份中國玩家過於「玻璃心」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-26-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.15.42-869x900.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-26-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.15.42-869x900.png&h=1512d1a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0d722f714b40e52b7ddda6d49646724e248c1d8","tid":1944345,"uid":78470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:15:40.000Z","msg":"隻game明明係大陸唔比玩<br />\n偷玩仲咁大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f16ffdb106884c63b435fef08cc516562c0e63b","tid":1944345,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"幾時先會有人嫌支那人麻煩唔鳩做佢地生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b01637fa248915aaed4ca71dafe4139b1661c8b","tid":1944345,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:18:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支那狗玩乜鳩Game吖，隻隻淨係日日玩賓周都忙到冇時間啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"33e54e436683b44d64f660965de7c4613deb5b47","tid":1944345,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"8964"},{"pid":"be9e2dc3fe82f4b7a36e0326ce4e1a13207b74a4","tid":1944345,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"期待正式版轉用8964做密碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678f7fc05079bf30cb9d7f24965b3ca1832409d2","tid":1944345,"uid":91511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />0-9都有中國啲衰野喎 不如唔好用數字啦"}]}